        "headline": "USN-8077-1: Bleach vulnerabilities",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "It was discovered that Bleach did not properly sanitize URI attributes containing character entities. An attacker could possibly use this issue to construct a URI with a disallowed scheme that would bypass sanitization, leading to cross-site scripting. This issue only affected Ubuntu 18.04 LTS. (CVE-2018-7753) Yaniv Nizry discovered that Bleach was vulnerable to a mutation cross-site scripting issue when sanitizing HTML with the noscript tag and a raw tag in the allowed tags list. An...",
          "lang": "en"
